++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Program 1 – Write a Ansible Adhoc Commands to create a group called “deploy"
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

[ec2-user@ip-172-31-11-15 ~]$ sudo ansible localhost -m group -a"state=present name=deploy"
localhost | CHANGED => {
    "changed": true,
    "gid": 1001,
    "name": "deploy",
    "state": "present",
    "system": false
}

[ec2-user@ip-172-31-11-15 ~]$ sudo ansible localhost -m group -a"state=present name=deploy"
localhost | SUCCESS => {
    "changed": false,
    "gid": 1001,
    "name": "deploy",
    "state": "present",
    "system": false
}
